-- Beijing Yanjing Brewery First-Half Profit Increases 25.2% on Higher Prices
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-21T10:03:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/beijing-yanjing-brewery-first-half-profit-increases-25-2-on-higher-prices.html

          
          
             Beijing Yanjing Brewery Co.’s first-
half net income increased 25.2 percent from a year earlier to
398.7 million yuan after the company raised prices for some beer
in January and focused on higher priced beers, according to a
statement to Shenzhen’s stock exchange.  
 First-half sales gained 2.9 percent to 5.04 billion yuan,
according to the statement.  
